<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="57" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Remark.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57">
<bibRefCitation author="Bae, YJ" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" refId="B1" refString="Bae, YJ, McCafferty, WP, 1991. Phylogenetic Systematics of the Potamanthidae (Ephemeroptera). Transactions of the American Entomological Society 117(3/4): 1-143." title="Phylogenetic Systematics of the Potamanthidae (Ephemeroptera). Transactions of the American Entomological Society 117 (3 / 4): 1 - 143." year="1991">Bae and McCafferty (1991)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" genus="R." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="R. distafurcus" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="distafurcus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">R. distafurcus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on imaginal specimens from Thailand, India, and Vietnam. The larva of 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" genus="R." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="R. distafurcus" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="distafurcus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">R. distafurcus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1076/0165-0424(200001)22:1;1-Z;FT009" author="Soldan, T" journalOrPublisher="Aquatic Insects" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" pagination="9 - 17" refId="B20" refString="Soldan, T, Putz, M, 2000. The larva of Rhoenanthus distafurcus Bae et McCafferty (Ephemeroptera: Potamanthidae) with notes on distribution and biology. Aquatic Insects 22 (1): 9 - 17, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1076/0165-0424(200001)22:1;1-Z;FT009" title="The larva of Rhoenanthus distafurcus Bae et McCafferty (Ephemeroptera: Potamanthidae) with notes on distribution and biology." url="https://doi.org/10.1076/0165-0424(200001)22:1;1-Z;FT009" volume="22" year="2000">Soldan T and Putz M (2000)</bibRefCitation>
based on specimens from Vietnam. In Thailand, a male adult of this species was found in Khao Yai National Park (
<bibRefCitation author="Bae, YJ" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" refId="B1" refString="Bae, YJ, McCafferty, WP, 1991. Phylogenetic Systematics of the Potamanthidae (Ephemeroptera). Transactions of the American Entomological Society 117(3/4): 1-143." title="Phylogenetic Systematics of the Potamanthidae (Ephemeroptera). Transactions of the American Entomological Society 117 (3 / 4): 1 - 143." year="1991">Bae and McCafferty 1991</bibRefCitation>
). In the present study, larval specimens of this species were found in western and northern Thailand.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
